#: ../../source/reference/learn/generated/maxframe.learn.preprocessing.scale.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.learn.preprocessing.scale"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:1 of
msgid "Standardize a dataset along any axis."
msgstr "沿任意轴标准化数据集。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:3 of
msgid "Center to the mean and component wise scale to unit variance."
msgstr "中心化到均值，并按分量缩放至单位方差。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:5 of
msgid "Read more in the :ref:`User Guide <preprocessing_scaler>`."
msgstr "更多内容请参见 :ref:`用户指南 <preprocessing_scaler>`。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:7 of
msgid "The data to center and scale."
msgstr "需要中心化和缩放的数据。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:9 of
msgid ""
"Axis used to compute the means and standard deviations along. If 0, "
"independently standardize each feature, otherwise (if 1) standardize each"
" sample."
msgstr ""
"用于计算均值和标准差的轴。如果为 0，则独立标准化每个特征，否则（如果为 1"
"）标准化每个样本。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:13 of
msgid "If True, center the data before scaling."
msgstr "如果为 True，则在缩放前对数据进行中心化。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:15 of
msgid ""
"If True, scale the data to unit variance (or equivalently, unit standard "
"deviation)."
msgstr "如果为 True，则将数据缩放至单位方差（或等效地，单位标准差）。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:18 of
msgid ""
"If False, try to avoid a copy and scale in place. This is not guaranteed "
"to always work in place; e.g. if the data is a numpy array with an int "
"dtype, a copy will be returned even with copy=False."
msgstr ""
"如果为 False，尝试避免复制并在原地缩放。但这不保证总是能在原地完成；例如"
"，如果数据是 int 类型的 numpy 数组，即使 copy=False，也会返回一个副本。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:24 of
msgid "**X_tr** -- The transformed data."
msgstr "**X_tr** -- 转换后的数据。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:29 of
msgid ":py:obj:`StandardScaler`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:30 of
msgid ""
"Performs scaling to unit variance using the Transformer API (e.g. as part"
" of a preprocessing :class:`~sklearn.pipeline.Pipeline`)."
msgstr ""
"使用 Transformer API 执行单位方差缩放（例如作为预处理的一部分 :class:`~"
"sklearn.pipeline.Pipeline`）。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:33 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:34 of
msgid ""
"This implementation will refuse to center scipy.sparse matrices since it "
"would make them non-sparse and would potentially crash the program with "
"memory exhaustion problems."
msgstr ""
"此实现将拒绝中心化 scipy.sparse 矩阵，因为这会使它们非稀疏化，并可能导致"
"程序因内存耗尽而崩溃。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:38 of
msgid ""
"Instead the caller is expected to either set explicitly `with_mean=False`"
" (in that case, only variance scaling will be performed on the features "
"of the CSC matrix) or to call `X.toarray()` if he/she expects the "
"materialized dense array to fit in memory."
msgstr ""
"调用者应显式设置 `with_mean=False`（这种情况下，仅对 CSC 矩阵的特征执行"
"方差缩放），或者如果他/她期望物化的密集数组能放入内存中，则调用 `X."
"toarray()`。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:43 of
msgid "To avoid memory copy the caller should pass a CSC matrix."
msgstr "为了避免内存复制，调用者应传递一个 CSC 矩阵。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:45 of
msgid ""
"NaNs are treated as missing values: disregarded to compute the "
"statistics, and maintained during the data transformation."
msgstr "NaN 被视为缺失值：在计算统计量时被忽略，并在数据转换过程中保留。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:48 of
msgid ""
"We use a biased estimator for the standard deviation, equivalent to "
"`numpy.std(x, ddof=0)`. Note that the choice of `ddof` is unlikely to "
"affect model performance."
msgstr ""
"我们使用有偏估计量计算标准差，等价于 `numpy.std(x, ddof=0)`。注意，`ddof`"
" 的选择不太可能影响模型性能。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:52 of
msgid ""
"For a comparison of the different scalers, transformers, and normalizers,"
" see: :ref:`sphx_glr_auto_examples_preprocessing_plot_all_scaling.py`."
msgstr ""
"有关不同缩放器、变换器和归一化器的比较，请参见：:ref:`sphx_glr_auto_"
"examples_preprocessing_plot_all_scaling.py`。"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:55 of
msgid "Risk of data leak"
msgstr "数据泄露风险"

#: maxframe.learn.preprocessing._data.standard_scaler.scale:57 of
msgid ""
"Do not use :func:`~sklearn.preprocessing.scale` unless you know what you "
"are doing. A common mistake is to apply it to the entire data *before* "
"splitting into training and test sets. This will bias the model "
"evaluation because information would have leaked from the test set to the"
" training set. In general, we recommend using "
":class:`~sklearn.preprocessing.StandardScaler` within a :ref:`Pipeline "
"<pipeline>` in order to prevent most risks of data leaking: `pipe = "
"make_pipeline(StandardScaler(), LogisticRegression())`."
msgstr ""
"除非你知道自己在做什么，否则不要使用 :func:`~sklearn.preprocessing.scale`"
"。一个常见的错误是在将数据分割为训练集和测试集 *之前* 应用它。这会导致"
"模型评估产生偏差，因为信息会从测试集泄露到训练集。通常，我们建议在 :ref:`"
"Pipeline <pipeline>` 中使用 :class:`~sklearn.preprocessing.StandardScaler"
"` 以防止大多数数据泄露风险：`pipe = make_pipeline(StandardScaler(), "
"LogisticRegression())`。"

